      "content": "i've tried everything. doctors, meds, therapy... nothing works. it's just a cycle of trying to manage the agony only for it to come back harder. it feels less like a \"struggle\" and more like a trap. sometimes i just stare at the wall and think about how much easier it would be if everything just stopped. if there was just... peace. without all this noise.",
